rall, loved this plugin 💜\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">This was actually awesome in a pinch</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/suicunesol/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/034acab7afd1ea51a842e79f923a0daa?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/034acab7afd1ea51a842e79f923a0daa?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/suicunesol/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">suicunesol</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">février 22, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I needed to make an FAQ page with accordians in less than an hour. This passed with flying colors. Cool beans, dudes.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Nice to use, need to be able to edit from product page</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rpollard/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/df186d3dcf21bdfeb14d7cfaa3c3a221?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/df186d3dcf21bdfeb14d7cfaa3c3a221?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rpollard/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">rpollard</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">janvier 6, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Like the FAQ plugin, it\'s easy to use.  However it would be useful to be able to edit an FAQ from the product page, rather than having to go through to the FAQs page to edit.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Superb</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/visionoptika/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4267b0212a0771a48ea84f6b83191902?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4267b0212a0771a48ea84f6b83191902?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/visionoptika/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Leonidas <small>(visionoptika)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 21, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Excellent support! Fast and accurate they solve my issue immediately.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great stuff, but needs Global and Per-Product FAQs</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/stwc/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/51f52f2688628413ec23f23723487bd5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/51f52f2688628413ec23f23723487bd5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/stwc/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">stwc</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">août 15, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">The plugin does everything it should, with no fuss, except for global and product-specific FAQs. I need to be able to have some FAQs that can appear on all products, but also item-specific ones (and I think others would too). That\'s doable currently of course, but will make for messy All FAQ lists in the backend with a large number of products.\n\nI notice there\'s a new \'cornerstone content\' tab in the admin All FAQs list, and I\'m guessing maybe that\'s what that is for, but I can\'t see a way to make it work (and it\'s not in the documentation that I can find), or exactly what it\'s for.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Best FAQ plugin for WooCommerce</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/surpriser/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0e16ffba8eda2189305092b0d0cf7792?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0e16ffba8eda2189305092b0d0cf7792?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/surpriser/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Surpriser</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">juillet 10, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I just tried many plugins for adding the faq tab to my products with schema support, and this is the only plugin at doo all of them for me. Thanks in Advance</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:157:\"Ultimate FAQ 